Union Berlin&rsquo;s manager Urs Fischer says Karius going back to Liverpool in January SHOULD NOT be an option, and that he is looking forward to keeping the goalkeeper and making him fight for his place starting January.<br />
<br />
The manager criticized the Union Berlin defenders saying they 'let him down' in his last match against SC Paderborn which they lost 3-2 and praised Karius by saying he &lsquo;did his thing well&quot;

